refsect2.para:
The GHashTable is synonymous with:
GHashTable *asv = g_hash_table_new_full (g_str_hash, g_str_equal, NULL, (GDestroyNotify) tp_g_value_slice_free);
Followed by manual insertion of each of the parameters.

